{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4accb39bdd","title":"机关文化大革命的重要性","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a140f2aa64","index":0,"year":1967,"month":1,"day":9,"articleId":"4accb39bdd"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji49","name":"毛泽东全集第49卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/49-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji49":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c6b5ac48a4","type":"title","text":"机关文化大革命的重要性","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"4accb39bdd"},{"id":"54fa51e916","type":"paragraph","text":"我们机关的文化大革命是非常重要的。如果只有学生运动、工人运动、农民运动，没有机关干部积极投入运动是不行的，好多重要问题靠机关干部亲自揭露。揭发是不可避免的。我们这个政府过去是由上面派去的少数干部和下面的绝大多数留用人员组成，不是工人、农民起来闹革命夺得了政府，这就很容易产生封建主义、修正主义的东西。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"4accb39bdd"}],"page":{"id":"c600bcdcfd","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"4accb39bdd","start":264,"end":264}}}},"__N_SSG":true}